<p>&#8216;The Court of Appeal has rejected an appeal over a High Court judge’s dismissal of a judicial review challenge to the Government’s decision to end the &#8220;Everyone In&#8221; initiative that was launched to get rough sleepers off the streets during the pandemic.&#8217;</p>
